zephyr-workbench.listRustToolchains.description:
List of registered Rust Toolchain entries (installed standalone or through rustup).
Each entry is an object { "toolchainPath": "...", "version": "...", "targets": ["thumbv7em-none-eabi", ...], "rustupToolchain": "stable|1.87.0 (rustup installs only)", "cToolchainType": "zephyr-sdk|gnuarmemb", "cToolchainPath": "...", "llvmPath": "..." }
llvmPath points to a host LLVM installation; its libclang directory is exposed as LIBCLANG_PATH for bindgen.
